 chain and strategic sourcing warehousing and logistics human resources information technology security and safety and regional finance and operations functions during goudis’ tenure as coo the company expanded its herbalife innovation and manufacturing him facilities to five locations around the world ensuring the highest levels of quality control for the company’s nutrition products under mr goudis’ management herbalife nutrition also grew its employee base to more than  people worldwide the company’s competitive advantage and success in the nutrition industry is based on science and education – sciencebased products and the education provided to customers by its distributors otherwise known as the “distributor difference” this difference has become more evident in recent years with retail stores closing at what seems to be an accelerated rate the educated and trained distributors meet facetoface with their customers providing personalized nutrition and fitness services newly appointed executive chairman michael o johnson draws from his extensive working history with goudis to say “the board and i could not have picked a more qualified candidate to lead this company forward we look forward to supporting him as he leads herbalife nutrition well into the future” to receive the latest company updates from herbalife nutrition follow herbalifenews about herbalife herbalife is a global nutrition company that has been changing people’s lives with great products since  our nutrition weightmanagement energy and fitness and personal care products are available exclusively to and through dedicated herbalife independent members in more than  countries we are committed to fighting the worldwide problems of poor nutrition and obesity by offering highquality products oneonone coaching with an herbalife member and a community that inspires customers to live a healthy active life we support the herbalife family foundation hff and its casa herbalife programs to help bring good nutrition to children in need we also sponsor more than  worldclass athletes teams and events around the globe including cristiano ronaldo the la galaxy and champions in many other sports the company has over  employees worldwide and its shares are traded on the new york stock exchange nyse hlf with net sales of approximately  billion in  to learn more visit herbalifecom or iamherbalifecom want to read the  reviews on herbalife click here for herbalife review live traffic our free newsletterget our free direct selling newsletter already  worldwide subscriberssubscribe now recent articles mary kay convention expects  attendees direct selling industry present for usa government steve carter achieves double president at world global network valentus  years in business  million in annual sales vern lapuz ariix vision award winner starbit international growth increases through crypto currency parties industry icon edward hartley passed away nerium international hosts world conference in st louis fuxion appoints jeff higginson as ceo international travis and summer flaherty achieved president rank at world global network popular articles industry icon edward hartley passed away  momentum ranks   solid top mlm companies for   top  worldwide earners in mlm – january   steve carter achieves double president at world global network  popular company reviews onecoin – onelife review  world global network review  jeunesse review  amway review  dox review  direct selling interviews vern lapuz ariix vision award winner interview with thanh duong from vietnam – onelife blue diamond north carolina couple’s total life changes success story interview with top leader miguel de oliveira – jeunesse interview with luana sicari cso starbit – the blockchain revolution facebook likes load more richard goudis herbalife ltd profile  biography  bloomberg feedback richard goudis chief executive officer herbalife ltd career history chief executive officer herbalife ltd present founder flamingo capita